<!doctype html>
<html lang="ru">
<head>
    <!-- Required meta tags -->
    <meta charset="utf-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1, shrink-to-fit=no">

    <!-- Bootstrap CSS -->
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="css/bootstrap.min.css">

    <title>Day 4 by @dylzo</title>

    <style>
        .bd-placeholder-img {
            font-size: 1.125rem;
            text-anchor: middle;
            -webkit-user-select: none;
            -moz-user-select: none;
            -ms-user-select: none;
            user-select: none;
        }

        @media (min-width: 768px) {
            .bd-placeholder-img-lg {
                font-size: 3.5rem;
            }
        }

        html {
            font-size: 14px;
        }

        @media (min-width: 768px) {
            html {
                font-size: 16px;
            }
        }

        .container {
            max-width: 960px;
        }

        .z-header {
            max-width: 700px;
        }

        .card-deck .card {
            min-width: 220px;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
<div class="d-flex flex-column flex-md-row align-items-center p-3 px-md-4 mb-3 bg-white border-bottom shadow-sm">
    <h5 class="my-0 mr-md-auto font-weight-normal">Day 4 - Ansible</h5>
</div>

<div class="z-header px-3 py-3 pt-md-5 pb-md-4 mx-auto text-center">
    <h1 class="display-4">Задание</h1>
    <p class="lead">Сгенерировать index.html из шаблона, который должен заполняться переменными: ansible_host, inventory_hostname и датой генерации шаблона.</p>
</div>

<div class="container">
    <div class="card-deck mb-3 text-left">
        <div class="card mb-4 shadow-sm">
            <div class="card-header">
                <div class="row">
                    <div class="col-md-5 item">
                        <h4 class="my-0 font-weight-normal">Generated:</h4>
                    </div>
                    <div class="col-md-6 offset-md-1 item text-right">
                        <h4 class="my-0 font-weight-normal text-muted">{{ lookup('pipe','date "+%H:%M:%S / %d.%m.%Y"') }}</h4>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="card-body">
                <ul class="list-unstyled mt-2 mb-2">
                    <li>Ansible Host: {{ ansible_host }}</li>
                    <li>Inventory Hostname: {{ inventory_hostname }}</li>
                </ul>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <footer class="pt-4 my-md-5 pt-md-3 border-top">
        <div class="row">
            <div class="col-12 offset-md-4">
                <small class="d-block mb-3 text-muted">Стажировка - Лига Цифровой Экономики &copy; 2020</small>
            </div>
        </div>
    </footer>
</div>
</body>
</html>
